> np.ndarray:\n    return (item + np.sqrt(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.cos(np.pi * (item / bins))\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item * np.exp(item - bins)) + np.tan(np.pi * (item / bins))\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item + np.log(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins))\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item * (np.max(bins) / bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.cos(np.pi * (item / bins))\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item + np.sqrt(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.tan(np.pi * (item / bins))\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item * (bins / (item + 1))) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins)) \n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item * (np.max(bins) - np.min(bins))) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins))\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item * (bins / (item + 1))) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins)) \n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    remaining = bins.max() - bins\n    return np.exp(-remaining) + np.exp(-item)\n```\n\n### Implementation 2: Logarithmic Remaining Space\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    remaining = bins.max() - bins\n    return np.log(remaining + 1) + np.log(item + 1)\n```\n\n### Implementation 3: Sine of Remaining Space\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    remaining = bins.max() - bins\n    return np.sin(remaining) + np.sin(item)\n```\n\n### Implementation 4: Square Root of Remaining Space\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    remaining = bins.max() - bins\n    return np.sqrt(remaining) + np.sqrt(item)\n```\n\n### Implementation 5: Ratio of Remaining Space to Item Size\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    remaining = bins.max() - bins\n    return (remaining / (item + 1)) + (item / (bins.max() + 1))\n```\n\n### Implementation 6: Combined Logarithmic and Exponential\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    remaining = bins.max() - bins\n    return np.log(remaining + 1) * np.exp(item)\n```\n\n### Implementation 7: Sine of Remaining Space and Item Size\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    remaining = bins.max() - bins\n    return np.sin(remaining) * np.sin(item)\n```\n\n### Implementation 8: Square Root of Remaining Space and Item Size\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    remaining = bins.max() - bins\n    return np.sqrt(remaining) * np.sqrt(item)\n```\n\n### Implementation 9: Ratio of Remaining Space and Item Size with Logarithm\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    remaining = bins.max() - bins\n    return (np.log(remaining + 1) / (item + 1)) + (np.log(item + 1) / (remaining + 1))\n```\n\n### Implementation 10: Combined Exponential and Logarithmic\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\ndef priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    remaining = bins.max() - bins\n    return np.exp(np.log(remaining + 1) + item)\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item + np.mean(bins) + np.std(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins))\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item + np.sort(bins)[-1]) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins))\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return np.exp(item) * 